reviewText:
I am simply delightful of possibility to buy the box containing Adventures of ARSENE LUPIN not only in nature as well as in Original
French Version. I am still interested in purchasing the Volume No. 2, but not yet because I am obliged to get due amount of
money for mine and my mummy staying in resting house in CIECHOCINEK. As this holiday is expensive enough, I return to this idea
in September, I think. In meantime, I wish to decline that AMAZON make me so happy man and let me realize my the biggest DREAMS !
